headline.print_headline: Ludogorets Make History With 1-0 Win Over Basel
headline.main: Ludogorets Make History With 1-0 Win Over Basel

lead_paragraph: An unstoppable last-gasp shot from defender Yordan Minev gave Ludogorets a 1-0 victory over 10-man Basel on Wednesday as they became the first Bulgarian team to register a Champions League group stage victory.
